        "key": "蠍爪鉗擊",
        "title": "蠍爪鉗擊",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_8419504271689793415.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>普通攻擊</color>\n造成2點 <color=#ffffff>物理傷害</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "蠍尾錐刺",
        "title": "蠍尾錐刺",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/86ad2f9a487b5e1fc7f14c6d3aebf17a_5163084852052078959.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素戰技</color>\n造成3點 <color=#ffacff>雷元素傷害</color> 。\n生成1張 <color=#ffffff>噬骸能量塊</color> ，隨機置入我方牌庫頂部2張卡牌之中。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "雷錐散射",
        "title": "雷錐散射",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/aebba01f5c8d920339645f679cd512aa_4999544917522289568.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素爆發</color>\n造成3點 <color=#ffacff>雷元素傷害</color> ， <color=#ffffff>捨棄</color> 手牌中最多3張 <color=#ffffff>噬骸能量塊</color> ，在對方場上生成 <color=#ffffff>雷錐陷阱</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>雷錐陷阱</color>\n<color=#ffd780>出戰狀態</color>\n<color=#ffffff>所在陣營的角色使用技能後：</color> 對所在陣營的出戰角色造成2點 <color=#ffacff>雷元素傷害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數：</color> 初始為建立時所棄置的 <color=#ffffff>噬骸能量塊</color> 張數。（最多疊加到3）"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "不朽亡骸‧雷",
        "title": "不朽亡骸‧雷",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/2f5fbc2acab943dc5e598980c758f964_6280095560220086256.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>被動技能</color>\n【被動】回合結束時，生成2張 <color=#ffffff>噬骸能量塊</color> ，隨機置入我方牌庫頂部10張卡牌之中。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "噬骸能量塊",
        "title": "噬骸能量塊",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_254642361481936235.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>事件牌</color>\n隨機 <color=#ffffff>捨棄</color> 1張原本元素骰費用最高的手牌，生成1個我方出戰角色類型的元素骰。（每回合最多打出1張）"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": [],
        "talentImg": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/531ed6322b0a8f721e6080da7fcd72ce_6024861274468479595.png"
      },
      {
        "key": "雷元素傷害",
        "title": "雷元素傷害",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_8232073347790368758.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "附著 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> ，可發生元素反應：\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>超載</color> ：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>超導</color> ：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點 <color=#ffffff>穿透傷害</color>\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#80c0ff>水元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>感電</color> ：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點 <color=#ffffff>穿透傷害</color>\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#99ff88>草元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>原激化</color> ：本傷害+1，生成「 <color=#ffffff>激化領域</color> 」\n<color=#ffffff>激化領域</color>\n<color=#ffd780>出戰狀態</color>\n我方對敵方出戰角色造成 <color=#ffacff>雷元素傷害</color> 或 <color=#99ff88>草元素傷害</color> 時，傷害值+1。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數：2</color>"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "規則解釋",
        "title": "規則解釋",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_4836527869373395641.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffffff>物理傷害</color>\n物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數</color>\n此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次 <color=#ffffff>可用次數</color> ；\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數</color> 耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。\n<color=#ffffff>捨棄</color>\n透過行動牌或角色技能的效果，將行動牌從手牌或牌庫中棄置。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      }
    ]
